article.headline: Kendal Coleman, AJ Braun score 17 apiece to help Cal Baptist defeat Incarnate Word 83-78 in opener
article.description: — Kendal Coleman and AJ Braun scored 17 points apiece to help California Baptist defeat Incarnate Word 83-78 in a season opener on Monday night.
article.linkText: Kendal Coleman, AJ Braun score 17 apiece to help Cal Baptist defeat Incarnate Word 83-78 in opener
article.story: RIVERSIDE, Calif. -- — Kendal Coleman and AJ Braun scored 17 points apiece to help California Baptist defeat Incarnate Word 83-78 in a season opener on Monday night. Coleman had six rebounds for the Lancers (1-0). Braun made 7 of 11 from the field and 3 for 6 from the line with five rebounds. Dominique Daniels Jr. shot 5 of 13 from the field and 6 for 9 from the line to finish with 16 points. The Cardinals were led by Davion Bailey, who recorded 41 points. Jalin Anderson added 20 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
